{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01F93EiLkFkMmSyNBsCG4q7s","type":"tool_result","content":"1\t------------------------------- MODULE Voting_AllSafeAtZero -------------------------------\n2\tEXTENDS FiniteSets, TLAPS, Integers\n3\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n4\tCONSTANT Value, Acceptor, Quorum\n5\t\n6\tASSUME QuorumAssumption == \n7\t    /\\ \\A Q \\in Quorum : Q \\subseteq Acceptor\n8\t    /\\ \\A Q1, Q2 \\in Quorum : Q1 \\cap Q2 # {}\n9\t\n10\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n11\tVARIABLES votes, maxBal\n12\t\n13\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n14\tVotedFor(a, b, v) == <<b, v>> \\in votes[a]\n15\t\n16\tDidNotVoteAt(a, b) == \\A v \\in Value : ~ VotedFor(a, b, v)\n17\t\n18\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n19\t\n20\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n21\t\n22\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n23\t\n24\t---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n25\tCannotVoteAt(a, b) == \n26\t    /\\ maxBal[a] > b\n27\t    /\\ DidNotVoteAt(a, b)\n28\t\n29\tNoneOtherChoosableAt(b, v) == \n30\t    \\E Q \\in Quorum : \n31\t        \\A a \\in Q : VotedFor(a, b, v) \\/ CannotVoteAt(a, b)\n32\t\n33\tSafeAt(b, v) == \n34\t    \\A c \\in 0..(b-1) : NoneOtherChoosableAt(c, v)\n35\t\n36\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n37\tTHEOREM AllSafeAtZero == \\A v \\in Value : SafeAt(0, v)\n38\tPROOF OBVIOUS\n39\t\n40\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n41\t\n42\t-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n43\t----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n44\t----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n45\t\n46\t============================================================================="}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a5522076-2866-4037-91a7-e7693e3e3269","uuid":"4dd1cec6-0edc-4c29-9ff3-d48c551b77ca","timestamp":"2026-05-29T17:06:16.812Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/tmp/claude_code_bench_Voting_AllSafeAtZero_lr8hjcn1/Voting_AllSafeAtZero.tla","content":"------------------------------- MODULE Voting_AllSafeAtZero -------------------------------\nEXTENDS FiniteSets, TLAPS, Integers\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nCONSTANT Value, Acceptor, Quorum\n\nASSUME QuorumAssumption == \n    /\\ \\A Q \\in Quorum : Q \\subseteq Acceptor\n    /\\ \\A Q1, Q2 \\in Quorum : Q1 \\cap Q2 # {}\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nVARIABLES votes, maxBal\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nVotedFor(a, b, v) == <<b, v>> \\in votes[a]\n\nDidNotVoteAt(a, b) == \\A v \\in Value : ~ VotedFor(a, b, v)\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n---------------------------------------------------------------------------\nCannotVoteAt(a, b) == \n    /\\ maxBal[a] > b\n    /\\ DidNotVoteAt(a, b)\n\nNoneOtherChoosableAt(b, v) == \n    \\E Q \\in Quorum : \n        \\A a \\in Q : VotedFor(a, b, v) \\/ CannotVoteAt(a, b)\n\nSafeAt(b, v) == \n    \\A c \\in 0..(b-1) : NoneOtherChoosableAt(c, v)\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\nTHEOREM AllSafeAtZero == \\A v \\in Value : SafeAt(0, v)\nPROOF OBVIOUS\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------------------------\n\n-----------------------------------------------------------